    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>As one whose immigrant father came to this country in 1910 and with his own energy and intelligence succeeded in a free-market economy, I could not agree more with Mr. Forstmann. More and more Government interference -- as opposed to private initiative -- will eventually fail, as we saw in the great Russian experiment of 70 years.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>As one whose immigrant father came to this country in 1910 and with his own energy and intelligence succeeded in a free-market economy, I could not agree more with Mr. Forstmann. More and more Government interference -- as opposed to private initiative -- will eventually fail, as we saw in the great Russian experiment of 70 years.</p>
        <p>Here's hoping, Mr. Forstmann, for a victory celebration Tuesday evening. NATHAN EIGES  New York City, Oct. 26</p>
      </block>
